    TraceArchiveWriter
    TraceArchiveWriter is a class that can write out a complete Trace Archive folder structure which contains the following files: TRACEINFO.XML README fasta folder: contains 1 fasta file per record pos folder: contains 1 position fasta file per record qual folder: contains 1 quality fasta file per record traces folder: contains 1 binary trace per record

    TraceArchiveWriter.TraceArchiveRecordDataException
    TraceArchiveRecordDataException is a checked Exception that is to be thrown when an error occurs while creating metadata for a TraceArchiveRecord.
